# Inkbox Agent Identity

- This project uses the Inkbox identity `@outreach-agent`.
- Primary mailbox: `hirepilot_outreach@inkboxmail.com`.
- Use the sender name `Chloe` unless the user asks for a different signature.
- Load the API key from `.env` via `INKBOX_API_KEY`; never hardcode or commit it.
- Prefer the Python Inkbox SDK for product code and use the CLI for manual mailbox inspection if needed.
- When sending on behalf of this agent, default to the configured handle from `.env` or the project defaults.
- The default human contact for the quickstart intro email is `chloezzx@bu.edu`.
- Approved outreach should default to the review inbox unless live sending is explicitly enabled.
